name: Articuno
ability_text: Boosts evasiveness if it is hailing or snowing.
description: It's said that this Pok√©mon's beautiful blue wings are made of ice. Articuno flies over snowy mountains, its long tail fluttering along behind it.

name: American Robin
description: The American Robin injests still-burning coals from abandoned campfires to help with its digestion.

name: Greater roadrunner
ability_text: Absorbs the harsh sunlight and gains the fire typing
description: Roadrunner can reach sustained speeds of 30km/hr. In intense sunshine, it gains the fire typing.

name: California Quail
ability_text: Defensive maneuver to blend into trees, bushes, or grass
description: Stocky bodies with long, pointed wings, often brown and a warm buffy orange

name: Wild Turkey
ability_text: Spectral sensitivity to wavelengths near 400 nanometers, allowing for enhanced eyesight.
description: Dark and bronze-green coloring with iridescence to most of their plumage.

name: Northern Cardinal
ability_text: A loud string of clear down-slurred or two-parted whistles, often speeding up and ending in slow trills.
description: Small birds, males are a bright red and females a brown color, both with pointed crests.
